{"tid":2115700,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"細聽學生故事 理大如何培育出明日環球領袖?","createTime":"2020-07-19T16:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-30T06:30:01.000Z","uid":225931,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"7b7fe2f8cff548923ca935b28e23308ed2bae6f2","tid":2115700,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T16:49:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/-/media/department/home/content/admission/student-stories/student-stories-478x540-madina.jpg?mh=540&amp;mw=478&amp;hash=EA89EF5635AC3A810EFD30CBEBD0A4AE\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fdepartment%2Fhome%2Fcontent%2Fadmission%2Fstudent-stories%2Fstudent-stories-478x540-madina.jpg%3Fmh%3D540%26mw%3D478%26hash%3DEA89EF5635AC3A810EFD30CBEBD0A4AE&h=001d7cda&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從服務中學習<br />\n理大的全人教育幫助我們掌握專業技能，令我得以貢獻世界。當中的服務學習課程和實習機會，讓我獲得寶貴的學習體驗。<br />\n<br />\n想在此分享我和同學在香港郊區的一個服務學習經歷，我們以推廣減廢為目標，一方面期望促進當地的生態旅遊，另一方面鼓勵旅客把自己的垃圾帶走。另外，我曾有機會在香港的政府基金及畢馬威會計師事務所實習，還參與過開展一個濾水處理的項目。<br />\n<br />\n由於在學期間經常接觸商業諮詢的工作，我期望未來也能在這個行業發展。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.polyu.edu.hk/-/media/department/home/content/admission/student-stories/student-stories-478x373-mac.jpg?mh=373&amp;mw=478&amp;hash=26A5F71C9F092E5DA40FB40CE91E3C40\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.polyu.edu.hk%2F-%2Fmedia%2Fdepartment%2Fhome%2Fcontent%2Fadmission%2Fstudent-stories%2Fstudent-stories-478x373-mac.jpg%3Fmh%3D373%26mw%3D478%26hash%3D26A5F71C9F092E5DA40FB40CE91E3C40&h=86df5ede&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n從新角度探索亞洲<br />\n我經常四處遊歷。在加拿大完成高中後，我熱切增加對亞洲的認識，很高興能在理大開展學習之旅。<br />\n<br />\n你會在宿舍和校園得到意想不到的跨文化體驗。我在理大其中一次最難忘的經歷，是和宿友合作主持理大首個非洲文化晚會。我甚至到了西班牙華倫西亞實習，為某公司剪輯錄像和經營社交媒體。<br />\n<br />\n理大為我提供了多方面的學習和發展機會，也擴展了我的視野。能夠和大學一起成長，是一次極寶貴的經驗，我熱切期待理大引領我再闖新天地。"},{"pid":"2e22c84fa62fc12c210d53f64123d6a4b74117bb","tid":2115700,"uid":68689,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T16:54:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3637825/org/43d72a4b9c569f77415d41c84259202b.jpg/aTbKTtFLyOv7fJWvf0r9HfyM8bcZaTyecTVbznE1W84?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3637825%2Forg%2F43d72a4b9c569f77415d41c84259202b.jpg%2FaTbKTtFLyOv7fJWvf0r9HfyM8bcZaTyecTVbznE1W84%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=3afcbc36&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fba60eed0bc738351b9c214d47f9670130c9f650","tid":2115700,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T17:07:05.000Z","msg":"poly好勁"},{"pid":"26653f1a4a99d8157b77ae6e0317f48c360b9732","tid":2115700,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:44:00.000Z","msg":"間間院校都話自己係全人教育, 有無第二句"},{"pid":"36c752dc3238ece8f6428dad8edccb220a832154","tid":2115700,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:46:35.000Z","msg":"條鬼仔成日著住多蒙特波衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eec2c20e56b202306a9b550dbdf9dfafa035b7b3","tid":2115700,"uid":28558,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T07:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/content/2019/1119/U655P22T1D795016F1DT20191119163039.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2Fcontent%2F2019%2F1119%2FU655P22T1D795016F1DT20191119163039.jpg&h=d02dc24e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.hkcna.hk/2019/1119/U655P22DT20191119161951.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkcna.hk%2F2019%2F1119%2FU655P22DT20191119161951.jpg&h=8c3d9177&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n理大我剩係記得抗黑警"},{"pid":"0bdc46a92ffccf5b6b0c5b344dc57018faf3bafb","tid":2115700,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-30T06:30:01.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}